                <h3>GUEST ROOMS</h3>
                <img src="https://rgmc.in/wp-content/themes/rgmc/club/images/stay/1.png" align="left">
                <p align="justify">The club has stay in facility of two rooms. It is a rare experience as they overlook D.P. cricket stadium Patiala which is reminiscent of The Oval, England. The ambience of these rooms has been taken care of and decor is traditional. The management has planned to add at least four more suites in near future. Food and beverages are available at regular club facilities. Room tariff for Members/Affiliated Clubs: Rs 1,500/- per night and for Foreign Nationals:	US$60 per night Check out time is 12:00 noon. Terms and conditions as applicable.</p>


