                <h3>PARTY ZONES</h3>
                <img src="https://rgmc.in/wp-content/themes/rgmc/club/images/party/3.png" align="left">
                <p align="justify">Majestic and Imperial Lounge are part of the heritage block of royal building where small parties and meetings can be held. Indoor booking for parties/meetings are also permitted in dining hall and vintage restobar. Outdoor, functions are allowed in Flower Valley Lawn close to swimming pool and also on the pool side. Loud music is not permitted. Indoor catering is by club only. Booking is strictly for club members only. Tariff plans for booking are available at club office.</p>
